      "type": "text",
      "id": "9ecc3adcc6d882c856c129cc0910c9b0",
      "source_id": "",
      "content": "WithÂ SubstanceÂ we are providing a technical foundation for solving these problems. It is a purely browser-based solution for document creation, ready to be integrated into various publication scenarios. We developed theÂ Substance Composer, a web-based editing environment andÂ eLife LensÂ an interactive display for scientific literature. Now we want to complement our solution with a decentralized hub for collaboration."
    },
